Sky (Percent)</td>
<td align="center">-</td>
</tr>
</table>

<P><HR><P>

<B>Next, </B> <%= date_selector_section %>
<P><HR><P>
<B>Finally, </B>select whether you want to view the data in your browser or download them
to a file, and click the "Download Data" button to obtain your data.

<BR/><input TYPE="radio" NAME="download_to_file" VALUE="false" CHECKED /> View data in browser
<BR/><input TYPE="radio" NAME="download_to_file" VALUE="true"/> Download directly to file
<P><input type="submit" value="Download Data">&nbsp&nbsp<input type="reset" value="Clear All Checkboxes">
</form>